2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in april##2
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |   5    |    6    |  7   |
| Birthday   | april | january | august | february | december | september | march |

