.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, comedy, thriller, documentary, fantasy, time-travel, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching action movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2   |     3     |      4      |      5      |   6    |      7       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | comedy | thriller | fantasy | action | superhero | documentary |

