.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-10::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, hedgehog, dog, snake, guinea-pig, fish
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the dog is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the dog##2
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | goldfish | hedgehog | fish | snake | dog | frog |

